channel.title: Portfowarding
channel.description: i cant seem to portfoward on my new internet connection with the new modem i got, the last one i had i portfowarded it perfectly and had my server running for a few months but now i got a new router and everything and it doesnt want to portfoward. i went to canyouseeme.org and put the ip it gave me in where it asks for my ip and it says 'Server IP address cannot be router's LAN IP address.' heres a pic of the setup it gives me: [IMG]http://i53.tinypic.com/33y6g40.png[/img] if anyone can help i would appreciate it very much. thx :)
